  "description": "<p><strong>Locum/Agency Staff Nurses</strong></p><p><strong>We are hiring </strong><u><strong>Locum/Agency Nurses</strong></u><strong> to be outsourced to reputable hospitals!</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Performs general nursing duties</li><li>Assist doctors in consultation rooms</li><li>Perform wound-dressing</li><li>Other ad hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Working hours:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Flexible OR Office Hours</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirement:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Valid SNB & BCLS required</li><li>Must be able to commit to 3 months or more </li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates can apply now by sending your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:recruitmedical@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>recruitmedical@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a><strong></strong></p><p>OR call <strong>Natashya</strong> at <strong>6736 3280</strong> for more enquiries.</p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Natashya Tasneem Thomas | Outsourcing Team | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
